{"tid":1151222,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)漢尼拔1-3","createTime":"2019-05-12T12:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T17:54:27.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"08e951fc65cef146bcbdff0cf49ee987ce871c8d","tid":1151222,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=1ae1e5c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=8cdea851\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=e1e5b3cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/94/The_Silence_of_the_Lambs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F94%2FThe_Silence_of_the_Lambs.jpg&h=1107bde0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/6b/Hannibal_movie_poster1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F6b%2FHannibal_movie_poster1.jpg&h=b5914d66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在FBI受訓的實習幹員克麗絲&middot;史達琳，奉局長傑克&middot;克勞福之命，前去探訪醫師漢尼拔&middot;萊克特以換得追尋連續殺人狂魔「野牛比爾」的線索。「野牛比爾」（一譯「水牛比爾」）是一個變態心理罪犯，犯下一連串殺人案件，並且剝下死者的皮，犯罪手法令人髮指<br />\n<br />\n2.電影開頭時已是上一集事件發生後10年，克莉絲&middot;史黛琳與手下正在想辦法攻入一名女毒犯的巢穴，而記者亦在現場等消息。幾經勸告後，毒犯與她的手下終於出來，但女毒犯懷中卻抱著她的嬰兒。最後，因同事的失誤，毒犯與FBI探員發生槍戰，女毒犯與其四名手下在鏡頭前被射殺，只留下在哭泣的嬰兒。司法部官員Paul Krendler（雷&middot;李歐塔飾）因以前對史黛琳求愛不遂，一直懷恨在心，現在即藉此機會報復，將整件事歸咎於史黛琳<br />\n<br />\n3.故事開頭是年輕的FBI探員威爾&middot;葛拉漢為了調查連續殺人案而前來拜訪合作夥伴：漢尼拔&middot;萊克特醫生，卻無意間發現漢尼拔就是那個連續殺人魔，葛拉漢被刺成重傷後仍不斷掙扎，在失去意識前對漢尼拔開槍，漢尼拔因此被捕。雖然威爾平安獲救，卻由於龐大的精神壓力而決定辭職，與妻兒住在佛羅里達的馬拉松<br />\n<br />\n9 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=ff30a8c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HaluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=4909d279\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a>"},{"pid":"77e26e989cbd0cebd6b07620bcd2d315f85f89b4","tid":1151222,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18ea20eab28d9d2d01aa5cf995004a2f96cf9bf","tid":1151222,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c